::DarkMouse::

Still shaking, she looks at Quickstrike,"All right. I'l tell him you 
got it all covered."  She looked down.  Something iside her didn't 
feel right.  She felt a power surge and her otics flashed brightly 
for a moment then returned to normal.  She looked at Black Aracnia.
"I'll do as you order."
